      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIGBAD FRANKY (1) hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran slick time when scoring over 388m at this track in 22.26. Has the ability and looks hard to top. MARG'S VOGUE (5) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at The Gardens the following run. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Can hit the frame this time. MY IRISH (7) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts two wins and three placings. Hit the frame latest (22.40) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. GAMBINO (2) placed here at this trip last start - cannot be ignored.",
